              <title>E-Design Template - Healthy Eating Model</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/11664</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/11664</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>I thought the e-Design template was clear and easy to understand, providing timings and task criteria for each action, rather like a rubric. Unlike the 4Ts model which I liked for its fluidity, I liked the e-Design model as it provided a "scaffold" upon which to build knowledge and understanding. There is the opportunity for both teacher-led and student-managed learning. The e-Design also helps you view the "bigger picture" in that it can provide an overview of progression as the course evolves.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>]]></description>
