              <description><![CDATA[<p>As we are working through H800 we are interested in encouraging our fellow students&nbsp; to actively particiate in online discussions.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Modern technologies offer amazing opportunities for collaboration and participation in the learning experience, but how can we ensure that all views are valued and everyone feels not only that they are welcome at the party, but that they want to be there?</p>]]></description>
